1
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:38,870
=Kebangkitan Zhao Jiadi=

2
00:00:38,870 --> 00:00:41,820
(Diadaptasi daripada "Out of His League" oleh Fenghuo Xizhuhou)

3
00:00:42,060 --> 00:00:44,940
=Episod 14=

4
00:00:46,680 --> 00:00:49,039
Saham di jalan komersial itu hanyalah langkah pertama.

5
00:00:49,399 --> 00:00:50,079
Selepas ini,

6
00:00:50,550 --> 00:00:52,679
masih banyak lagi pertempuran dengan Chen Hongxiong.

7
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:54,560
- Encik Baliang.
- Cai.

8
00:00:54,719 --> 00:00:55,840
Malas lagi ke?

9
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:57,479
Boleh tahan juga, kan?

10
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:58,399
Kau ni memang susah nak hilang.

11
00:00:58,399 --> 00:01:00,880
Cai, jangan salah faham.

12
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,799
Aku dulu bukan lawan kau sebab Yang Qingdi.

13
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:05,280
Tapi kali ini dengan Zhao Jiadi,

14
00:01:06,079 --> 00:01:07,519
aku takkan mengalah semudah itu.

15
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:09,439
Bukan itu maksud aku.

16
00:01:09,799 --> 00:01:10,920
Kenapa kau fikir terlalu jauh?

17
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:13,079
Jadi maksud kau

18
00:01:13,599 --> 00:01:14,599
dia boleh direbut?

19
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:16,840
Lagipun,

20
00:01:17,799 --> 00:01:18,680
Zhao Jiadi

21
00:01:19,319 --> 00:01:22,000
memang tak menepati piawaian ayah kau untuk menantu pun.

22
00:01:22,879 --> 00:01:25,280
Piawaian dia tak penting.

23
00:01:27,359 --> 00:01:29,599
Tapi aku tahu penilaian kau, Cai Yanzhi.

24
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,239
Ia takkan salah.

25
00:01:32,690 --> 00:01:33,719
Mari kita minum lagi.

26
00:01:46,250 --> 00:01:48,280
Green Leaf Tech benar-benar memainkan peranannya kali ini,

27
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,560
tapi saya tak dapat apa-apa sebagai pewarisnya.

28
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,719
Saya kecewa.

29
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:53,480
Jadi, apa yang kamu mahu?

30
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:57,519
Mari, habiskan minuman ini.

31
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,120
Kita anggap selesai.

32
00:01:59,319 --> 00:02:00,400
Saya akan biarkan saja.

33
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,680
Saya minum ini untuk Encik Baliang saya.

34
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:05,719
Baiklah.

35
00:02:08,090 --> 00:02:09,159
Tak cukup lagi. Ayuh.

36
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:10,520
Satu lagi gelas.

37
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:16,280
Kenapa pandang dia? Pandang saya.

38
00:02:28,719 --> 00:02:30,120
Minuman ini betul-betul kuat.

39
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,560
Tunggu, saya rasa pening.

40
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:36,719
Mungkin awak patut hantar dia balik.

41
00:02:37,439 --> 00:02:37,919
Baiklah.

42
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,520
Hantar saya balik.

43
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,560
Baring dulu.

44
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:42,479
Baring.

45
00:02:42,530 --> 00:02:43,280
Baringlah, cepat.

46
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,159
Selamat tinggal.

47
00:02:46,319 --> 00:02:47,039
Saya pun nak ikut!

48
00:02:47,159 --> 00:02:47,879
Saya nak balik!

49
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:48,840
Tunggu saya.

50
00:02:52,610 --> 00:02:53,360
Awak buat apa?

51
00:02:54,159 --> 00:02:55,520
Mesej Hongli, mestilah.

52
00:02:55,639 --> 00:02:56,520
Awak tak nampak ke?

53
00:02:56,599 --> 00:02:58,039
Dia yang kejar bos kita.

54
00:03:00,879 --> 00:03:01,639
Jangan mesej dia lagi.

55
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:12,840
Zhao Jiadi?

56
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:23,400
Oleh kerana kamu sudah di sini, jangan pergi.

57
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:25,759
Kamu mabuk. Pergilah berehat.

58
00:03:27,159 --> 00:03:29,000
Zhao Jiadi, adakah kamu di dalam?

59
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:38,879
Bukankah awak sepatutnya hantar dia pulang?
Kenapa awak masih di sini?

60
00:03:41,479 --> 00:03:43,840
Lambat betul awak sampai sini.

61
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,240
Di mana dia?

62
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:46,319
Di dalam.

63
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:49,280
Jaga dia. Saya nak keluar.

64
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:52,560
Kadang-kadang,

65
00:03:53,439 --> 00:03:54,479
Saya betul-betul tertanya-tanya...

66
00:03:57,439 --> 00:04:02,120
Kau betul-betul pelajar tahun ketiga universiti ke?

67
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:03,840
Kau mabuk.

68
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:12,080
Kau tunggu orang lain ke?

69
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,280
Mesti Chen Jiahao.

70
00:04:19,050 --> 00:04:20,000
Aku tak pesan apa-apa.

71
00:04:20,439 --> 00:04:21,279
(Yuan?)

72
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,600
Aku hantar makanan bakar kat sini.

73
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:24,720
Lepas tu...

74
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:27,639
Aku nampak kau dengan seorang perempuan mabuk

75
00:04:27,639 --> 00:04:28,639
masuk ke dalam bilik.

76
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:30,240
Aku belikan kau ubat mabuk.

77
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:31,279
Terima kasih.

78
00:04:33,319 --> 00:04:34,120
Baiknya kau.

79
00:04:38,079 --> 00:04:39,439
Konon nak tak campur tangan.

80
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,639
Tapi kau masuk campur juga separuh jalan.

81
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,360
Itu tak baik, tahu tak.

82
00:04:44,519 --> 00:04:46,240
Macam mana keadaan dia?

83
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:48,279
Dia okey.

84
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,959
Sebenarnya, saya datang nak beritahu awak sesuatu yang penting.

85
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:55,120
Masa saya sedang susun senarai CET-4,

86
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:57,120
Saya perasan nama awak tak ada dalam senarai.

87
00:04:58,040 --> 00:05:00,120
CET-4? Saya tak ambil peperiksaan tu.

88
00:05:04,199 --> 00:05:05,319
Satu lagi perkara.

89
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,879
Ini tentang Cik Jiang.

90
00:05:07,279 --> 00:05:09,120
Dia dapat tahu awak tak daftar untuk CET-4.

91
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,000
Dia sangat marah.

92
00:05:10,190 --> 00:05:11,680
Dia sedang cari awak di kampus.

93
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:12,839
Biarkan saja.

94
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:14,319
Dia takkan dapat tangkap saya pun.

95
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:15,959
Saya...

96
00:05:20,628 --> 00:05:21,240
Masuklah.

97
00:05:22,210 --> 00:05:23,480
Kalau awak suka seseorang, cakap saja.

98
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,680
Jujurlah dengan dia.

99
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,519
Ada apa-apa yang awak nak beritahu saya?

100
00:05:26,839 --> 00:05:27,800
Saya nak ucap terima kasih

101
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,480
untuk hari itu.

102
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,720
Sejak awak selesaikan hal dengan Zheng Kun,

103
00:05:31,730 --> 00:05:33,600
keadaan dalam majlis pelajar jadi lebih baik.

104
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,399
Pelajar dari keluarga susah

105
00:05:35,399 --> 00:05:36,800
tak lagi dipandang rendah.

106
00:05:39,199 --> 00:05:40,600
Saya cuma nak cakap...

107
00:05:41,079 --> 00:05:43,000
Tak bolehkah kita tidur waktu malam hujung minggu?

108
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,439
Ini pasti akan jadi seronok.

109
00:06:00,879 --> 00:06:01,879
Kenapa awak?

110
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:03,480
Apa yang awak buat di sini?

111
00:06:05,399 --> 00:06:06,759
Ponteng CET-4

112
00:06:07,279 --> 00:06:08,160
untuk daftar masuk hotel?

113
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,639
Dan kenapa awak ada di sini?

114
00:06:12,759 --> 00:06:14,240
Air di asrama kami terputus.

115
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,879
Beritahu saya, apa yang istimewa tentang Zhao Jiadi

116
00:06:15,879 --> 00:06:17,079
sampai semua orang suka padanya?

117
00:06:17,079 --> 00:06:19,439
Merepek. Dia guru kelas kita.

118
00:06:21,279 --> 00:06:21,959
Cikgu Jiang.

119
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:24,000
Awak datang sejauh ini

120
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,959
hanya untuk paksa saya ambil CET-4?

121
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:29,079
Zhao Jiadi, jaga sikap awak.

122
00:06:29,199 --> 00:06:30,240
Saya guru kelas awak.

123
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:32,519
Jiadi.

124
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:35,839
Zhao Jiadi?

125
00:06:36,839 --> 00:06:37,360
Siapa itu?

126
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,480
Jiadi?

127
00:06:39,759 --> 00:06:40,439
Teman wanita saya.

128
00:06:41,879 --> 00:06:42,879
Saya akan bercakap dengan awak nanti.

129
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:48,959
Sertai kami.
